title: Is the event over for OCE now? I only see normal rift and normal aram for modes now
body: I was in an aram match then it disconnected me and I tried logging back in and it said it's down for maintenance. Screenshot https://i.ibb.co/dJXx4Sb/que.png

replies.body: Yep, the event was only running through April Fool's, but us on OCE get things like this a little longer because of timezones.
